Get free icons in Windows 11 Filled design style

Windows 11 Filled is a bright flat icon pack. These color graphics will fit any desktop, web application, and mobile app screen.

As well as Cute Color, Hand Drawn Color, and Color icon packs, Windows 11 Filled icons effectively work as clipart images for infographics, custom cards, or presentations.

Download the color icons in different themes for your UI and graphic design needs. You can also edit the images you want right on the spot.

The free graphics are pixel-perfect and available in both PNG and vector.
